title: Counsel Me, Grantie
description:
Written by Kelly Hudson and James McCarthy
Starring: Kelly Hudson, Lisa Kleinman, Dan Hodapp, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, Zack Phillips, Alene Latimer

Directed by Jim Santangeli

Filmed at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, Oct. 15, 2012.

Filmed by Rob Michael Hugel, David Bluvband.
Edited by Rob Michael Hugel.
